WEBVTT

00:01.219 --> 00:03.161
<i>Previously on</i> Mike & Molly...

00:03.162 --> 00:04.762
Oh, I got in.

00:04.764 --> 00:06.798
Well, what is going
on with you?

00:06.800 --> 00:08.100
The Iowa Writers Workshop.

00:08.101 --> 00:10.068
I've been accepted into
their summer writing program.

00:10.069 --> 00:11.202
Wait a minute.

00:11.204 --> 00:14.071
Are you actually good
at this writing thing?

00:14.073 --> 00:16.375
I'll be living my dream
in Iowa for eight weeks.

00:16.376 --> 00:18.710
How are you gonna ruin that,
Peggy?

00:18.711 --> 00:19.911
Eight weeks?

00:19.913 --> 00:21.280
Does Mike know
about all this?

00:21.281 --> 00:23.681
Damn it, you always find a way.

00:24.850 --> 00:26.684
I have some exciting news.

00:26.686 --> 00:28.053
More for her than you.

00:28.054 --> 00:29.520
Shh!

00:29.522 --> 00:31.255
What is going on?

00:31.257 --> 00:33.759
I've been accepted into one
of the most prestigious

00:33.760 --> 00:35.593
writing programs in the country.

00:35.595 --> 00:37.062
Honey, that's great!

00:37.063 --> 00:39.230
In Iowa.

00:42.067 --> 00:43.568
It's an opportunity
of a lifetime.

00:43.569 --> 00:44.703
Well, I'm sure it is.

00:44.704 --> 00:46.605
I can't believe
you did this whole deal

00:46.606 --> 00:48.206
without even talking
to me about it.

00:48.207 --> 00:49.741
Well, we're talking
about it now.

00:49.742 --> 00:50.909
No, you're telling me.

00:50.910 --> 00:52.010
Talking about it would be,

00:52.011 --> 00:53.244
"Honey, I'm thinking
about applying

00:53.245 --> 00:54.813
"for an out-of-state workshop
for a couple months.

00:54.814 --> 00:55.980
You okay with that?"

00:55.982 --> 00:58.215
Are you okay with that?

00:59.250 --> 01:01.452
Why didn't you tell me?

01:02.721 --> 01:05.657
Just figured
I was never gonna get in.

01:05.658 --> 01:08.859
I was too embarrassed
to even talk about it.

01:10.195 --> 01:12.464
Lady, you have no idea

01:12.465 --> 01:14.465
how great you are.

01:14.467 --> 01:17.869
Smart and talented.

01:17.870 --> 01:23.508
Huh? And you can do anything
that you set that mind to.

01:23.509 --> 01:25.676
Thank you.

01:26.844 --> 01:29.681
I'm sorry I'm leaving you here
with the lunatics.

01:29.682 --> 01:31.482
The Taser's working, right?

01:31.483 --> 01:33.383
(laughing)
Yeah.

